---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import FeaturedVideo from "../video/FeaturedVideo";
import heroImg from "../../assets/img/beta/audacity-4-beta-hero.webp";
import envelopeImg from "../../assets/img/beta/audacity-4-beta-envelope.webp";
import labelsImg from "../../assets/img/beta/audacity-4-beta-labels.webp";
import spectrogramImg from "../../assets/img/beta/audacity-4-beta-spectrogram.webp";
import cloudProjectsImg from "../../assets/img/beta/audacity-4-beta-cloud-projects.webp";
---

<div class="my-6 space-y-16">
  <div class="space-y-4">
    <div
      class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-5 py-4 flex items-start gap-3"
    >
      <svg
        class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        fill="none"
        stroke="currentColor"
        stroke-width="1.5"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9.25"></circle>
        <line x1="12" y1="11" x2="12" y2="17" stroke-linecap="round"></line>
        <circle cx="12" cy="7.75" r="0.9" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"
        ></circle>
      </svg>
      <p class="text-gray-800">
        <strong>We're putting the finishing touches on the beta.</strong><br />
        Download links for Windows, macOS and Linux will land on this page very soon.
      </p>
    </div>

    <Image
      src={heroImg}
      alt="Audacity 4 beta: multitrack project view"
      class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-md"
    />

    <section>
      <p>
        We can't wait to get Audacity 4 into your hands. The beta is
        feature-complete with Audacity 3, with plenty already reworked and
        improved. Expect some bugs and quirks along the way, so keep your
        important projects in Audacity 3 for now.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3">
        When the beta lands, we'll point you to the best places to report bugs
        and share what you think.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>

  <section>
    <h2 class="text-2xl">What we've been working on</h2>
    <p class="mt-2">
      Here are the latest features that we can't wait for you to try.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div>
        <Image
          src={envelopeImg}
          alt="Envelope editing in Audacity 4 beta"
          class="aspect-video w-full object-cover rounded-md"
        />
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-base font-semibold">Envelope editing</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mt-1">
          Draw, drag, and reshape gain envelopes across clips with the
          redesigned envelope tool.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <Image
          src={labelsImg}
          alt="Label tracks in Audacity 4 beta"
          class="aspect-video w-full object-cover rounded-md"
        />
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-base font-semibold">Label tracks</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mt-1">
          Mark sections, drop chapter points, and keep your project organised as
          you work.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <Image
          src={spectrogramImg}
          alt="Spectral editing in Audacity 4 beta"
          class="aspect-video w-full object-cover rounded-md"
        />
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-base font-semibold">Spectral editing</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mt-1">
          Select frequency regions in the spectrogram and apply effects right
          where you need them.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <Image
          src={cloudProjectsImg}
          alt="Cloud projects and audio.com in Audacity 4 beta"
          class="aspect-video w-full object-cover rounded-md"
        />
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-base font-semibold">Cloud projects & audio.com</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mt-1">
          Save projects to the cloud and upload finished audio straight to
          audio.com.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <ul class="mt-8 divide-y divide-gray-200 border-y border-gray-200">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-4 py-4">
        <span class="icon icon-medium text-blue-700 icon-cycle shrink-0"></span>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900">
            Backwards compatibility
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mt-1">
            Audacity 3 projects open in Audacity 4, with your clips, tracks, and
            labels carried across.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-4 py-4">
        <span class="icon icon-medium text-blue-700 icon-monitor shrink-0"
        ></span>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900">
            Multi-project sessions
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mt-1">
            Open multiple projects, switch between them, and copy clips across.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-4 py-4">
        <span class="icon icon-medium text-blue-700 icon-note shrink-0"></span>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900">Metadata editor</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mt-1">
            Set track titles, artist, album, and other tags directly inside
            Audacity, ready for export.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-4 py-4">
        <span class="icon icon-medium text-blue-700 icon-mixer shrink-0"></span>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900">Effects</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mt-1">
            Polished effect UIs and quality-of-life improvements.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-4 py-4">
        <span class="icon icon-medium text-blue-700 icon-plug shrink-0"></span>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900">Plugin support</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mt-1">
            Nyquist, AudioUnits, and VST3 are supported across all platforms,
            with LV2 on Linux.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-4 py-4">
        <span class="icon icon-medium text-blue-700 icon-microphone shrink-0"
        ></span>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900">
            Lead-in recording
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mt-1">
            Previously punch and roll. Record over a section without losing what
            comes after
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="text-2xl">Deprecated features</h2>
    <p class="mt-2">
      A handful of things from Audacity 3 aren't coming with us. Tempo tracks,
      LADSPA, and Vamp analyzers won't be in Audacity 4.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="text-2xl">While you wait</h2>
    <p class="mt-2">
      A behind-the-scenes look at how we're rebuilding Audacity.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6">
      <FeaturedVideo
        client:load
        placeholderImage="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/QYM3TWf_G38/maxresdefault.jpg"
        imageAltText="Video thumbnail: How we're building Audacity 4"
        videoURL="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/QYM3TWf_G38?autoplay=1"
        matomoEventName="How we're building Audacity 4"
      />
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
